node.title: Grammys 2022: The hottest looks from the Grammys red carpet
node.description: From Justin Bieber to Lady Gaga, here's who showed up in a big way
node.content: ["Yep, red carpets are having a comeback moment. After years of COVID-19 setbacks that kept glamor to a minimum, the 64th Annual Grammy Awards, set in glitzy Las Vegas, offered entertainers a chance to get bold, and did they ever.", "From veteran DJs to this year's country-pop it girls, here's who showed up -- and showed up big."]
